stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Resolved
    Resolved --> Validated: registry, authority, target and renderer checks pass
    Resolved --> Abandoned: resolution or validation fails
    Validated --> Computed: renderer returns valid payload
    Computed --> PlanCaptured: immutable plan and identity captured
    Computed --> Abandoned: output violates target semantics
    PlanCaptured --> Abandoned: any captured guard drifts
    PlanCaptured --> Locked: preflight passes and workspace lock acquired
    Locked --> Abandoned: under-lock revalidation fails
    Locked --> WrittenUnverified: atomic write and byte verification succeed
    Locked --> Abandoned: write or verification fails
    WrittenUnverified --> Accepted: DPA-500 gate set succeeds
    WrittenUnverified --> Abandoned: gate set rejects refresh instance
    Accepted --> [*]
    Abandoned --> [*]
